                <div class="box">
                    <img class="img-responsive center-block" style="padding:15px; height:150px;" src="~/Images/MCSD-App-Builder-logo-Blk.png" />
                    <h3>Microsoft Certified Solutions Developer: App Builder</h3>
                    <p><small>Sep 2016</small></p>
                    <p class="description">The Microsoft Certified Solutions Developer (MCSD): App Builder certification validates the skills needed to build modern web applications and services.</p>
                    <p></p>
                    <p class="read-more"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/learning/mcsd-app-builder-certification.aspx">Read more <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 item" style="min-height: 450px;">
                <div class="box">
                    <img class="img-responsive center-block" style="height:150px;" src="~/Images/PSMI.png" />
                    <h3>Scrum.Org: Professional Scrum Master (PSM I)</h3>
                    <p><small>Feb 2016</small></p>
                    <p class="description">The Professional Scrum Master level I (PSM I) assessment validates the depth of knowledge of the Scrum framework and its application.</p>
                    <p></p>
                    <p class="read-more"><a href="https://www.scrum.org/Assessments/Professional-Scrum-Master-Assessments/PSM-I-Assessment">Read more <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

