                    <p><small>Dec 2013, Re-certified December 2015</small></p>
                    <p class="description">The Microsoft Certified Solutions Developer (MCSD): Web Applications certification validates the skills needed by a web developer or web administrator.</p>
                    <p></p>
                    <p class="read-more"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/learning/mcsd-web-apps-certification.aspx">Read more <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 item" style="min-height: 450px;">
